## Limitations

The findings presented in this report are based on available literature and may not capture all nuances of the topic. Some studies may have methodological limitations, such as small sample sizes or cultural biases. Additionally, the influence of social and cultural factors on psychological differences is complex and may not be fully accounted for in all studies. Further research is needed to explore the interplay between biological, social, and cultural influences on psychological differences between men and women.

